parameters:
[Anastasia] (If only I could use sorcery, I could easily erase those
memories.)

[Anastasia] (And the time I have to act is decreasing moment by
moment... There is no longer a moment's respite...)
[Gisellemina] Oh my~ What's wrong with that face?

[Gisellemina] I'm not always cooped up inside the mansion, you know~
Sometimes I go out too.

[Gisellemina] More importantly, that face... It's like you've been
caught doing something embarrassing, isn't it? Teehee~
[Gisellemina] Hehehe, I wonder if someone caught you masturbating?

[Gisellemina] You couldn't resist and ended up masturbating outdoors,
and someone saw you~

[Gisellemina] Sometimes, while I'm in the middle of taking care of my
business, a man from the inn walks in on me~
[Anastasia] Ugh... It's all because of your sorcery, that I...

[Gisellemina] Please stop saying things like It's as if I became
addicted to masturbation because of your sorcery.

[Gisellemina] It's really within the range of your pre-existing sexual
desire, you know~.

[Gisellemina] You were probably doing it every day even before you were
under the spell, right?

[Gisellemina] Well, it seems like even that masturbation of yours is
reaching its limit~
[Gisellemina] I've come to give you some advice.
[Anastasia] Y-You were the one behind it after all.

[Gisellemina] Hehehe, how rude of you to say such unpleasant things
after I came all this way to give you advice.
[Gisellemina] Hehehe, even you seem to be at your wit's end.

[Gisellemina] Well, it's quite a wise decision to stay silent and
listen here, I suppose~.

[Gisellemina] Well, even if you speak with an attitude, I'll still give
you advice, so don't worry.

[Gisellemina] There's actually a way to suppress your sexual desire,
you know~?

[Gisellemina] Well, it's just that you didn't seem interested, so I
didn't say it~

[Gisellemina] If you can collect a man's... semen, you can return to
your original form, ohhh~
[Anastasia] T-There's no way something like that is possible!

[Gisellemina] By the way, you can also recover a little bit of magical
power, but too bad~

[Gisellemina] Well, if you're fine just the way you are, then I don't
mind at all.

[Gisellemina] And then, all that's left is for you to come to the
mansion to defeat me...

[Gisellemina] Of course, I have my servants protecting me. I doubt that
you, in your current state and without magic, can defeat me or even my
servants before me.

[Gisellemina] Well, do your best to collect the semen of men and
recover your magical power~
[Anastasia] T-There's no way something like that is possible...

[Anastasia] ...There's still no sign of support coming from the
capital...
[Anastasia] Where on earth have you been until now?!

[Principal] Oh, I'm terribly sorry. I was suddenly called to the
capital...

[Principal] However, as expected of Anastasia-sama. While I was absent
for a little while, you managed to find the missing students.

[Principal] Yes, everyone has returned safely... During the time they
were kidnapped, they said they saw Anastasia-sama fighting by their
side.

[Principal] Surely, the culprit must have thought that Anastasia-sama
had been defeated.

[Principal] There are still unclear aspects regarding the motive of the
incident... However, the students were unharmed, and you also
protected the reputation of the academy.

[Principal] I suppose we can say that things have settled down. I truly
cannot thank you enough, Anastasia-sama. As a token of our gratitude,
we will send our thanks to the capital later.
[Principal] I'm glad it was resolved so quickly.

[Principal] Even though you must have been worried about your father,
Anastasia-sama, you managed to handle this situation...
[Anastasia] Is something wrong with my father?

[Principal] Oh? Could it be that you still don't know?! That's
terrible.

[Principal] Chairman... Um, it seems that some kind of misconduct was
found regarding Anastasia-sama's father, and he has resigned from the
position of chairman...

[Principal] Actually, because of that, I was absent from the academy
for a while.

[Principal] Anastasia-sama, I thought that once the missing person
incident was resolved, you would immediately return to the capital...

[Anastasia] (The father I know is not someone who would engage in any
wrongdoing.)

[Anastasia] (It's too coincidental that my father fell from grace at
the same time I was cursed.)

[Anastasia] (There's no doubt that someone is scheming behind the
scenes.)

[Anastasia] (And, there's no doubt that the principal is involved in
this. No, it's even possible to consider that the principal is leading
this.)

[Anastasia] (Because of the curse as well... I can't leave this town
right now. However... in order to do that...)
[Anastasia] No, I am thinking of staying in this town for a while.

[Anastasia] It is concerning that there are allegations of misconduct
against my father... However, that is something that happened to my
father. It is not something for me, his daughter, to get involved in.

[Anastasia] U-um, there's something I'd like to ask... I would like to
borrow a room at this inn for a little while longer.
[Principal] To be honest... the rooms at that inn are not cheap...

[Principal] As the headmaster of the academy, even though the students
have returned and the incident has been resolved, we cannot continue
to borrow for an indefinite period of time.

[Principal] I do feel sorry for not being able to be of help to you,
Anastasia-sama, especially considering that the chairman ended up in
such a situation...
[Anastasia] (Y-You see, it didn't go as smoothly as I thought.)

[Anastasia] (However, this situation is worse than I thought. I have
very few resources left...)

[Anastasia] (In my current state, I can't even return to the capital...
and I can't rely on support from my father...)

[Anastasia] I-It can't be helped... Then, at least another cheap
room...
